title: Eco Chic Recycled Dog Lead Double Sided Reflective Machine Washable Pet Leash (Highland Cow Teal Medium/Large)
features: ENHANCED SAFETY - Includes reflective stitching for increased visibility during nighttime walks, ensuring your dog's safety in low-light conditions.
FASHIONABLE AND STYLISH - Available in a range of colourful designs to suit your dog's personality and any occasion.
DURABLE HARDWARE - Features a strong, stainless steel metal clasp for a secure attachment to your dog's collar or harness.
ECO-FRIENDLY - Each lead is made from the equivalent of eight recycled plastic bottles, contributing to environmental sustainability.
MATCHING ACCESSORIES - Complete your dog's look with matching bandanas, collars and harnesses also available!

Matching Set – Complete the look with coordinating harnesses, collars, and bandanas. Our Mission Help everyone adapt to using Recyclable, Reusable and Sustainable products.
